{"000-section": {"000-title": "ova.gov.in \u2013 Odia Virtual Academy (OVA) Website Launched by CM Odisha"}, "001-section": {"000-title": "Odisha CM launches Odia Virtual Academy website ova.gov.in to preserve resources of Odia language & culture of the state, OVA portal contains library, magazines, dictionary, info. on cultural dance & music and even translation for Odia language"}, "002-section": {"000-title": "Odia Virtual Academy Website", "001-normal": "The primary objectives behind the launch of Odia Virtual Academy websites are as follows:-", "002-listElement": "- To digitize approx. 2000 rare and copyright free books and to establish a free digital library.", "003-listElement": "- To digitize various dictionaries which are presently available and to upload such dictionaries on Odia Virtual Academy website for free access to citizens.", "004-listElement": "- Promotion of Odia unicode fontfaces by standardization of typing keyboards and to make them affordable for general public in the next 6 months.", "005-listElement": "- To develop primers and their uploading on Odia Virtual Academy to ensure easy learning and speaking of Odia language by English, French, German, Japanese and Spanish people.", "006-normal": "Dedicated Odia Virtual Academy website which hosts rich repository of digital version of our rare literary works. It will help researchers, language lovers and especially youngsters staying all over the world to read our magnificent literary works<https://t.co/uuvNF0y5bb> [pic.twitter.com/hghwF5aaCb](https://t.co/hghwF5aaCb)", "007-normal": "\u2014 Naveen Patnaik (@Naveen\\_Odisha) [October 27, 2018](https://twitter.com/Naveen_Odisha/status/1056043745269805056?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw)", "008-normal": "", "009-normal": "All the details regarding Odia language are present at the official [ova.gov.in](http://ova.gov.in/en/) which will provide all the necessary information about the language."}, "003-section": {"000-title": "Purpose of Odia Virtual Academy", "001-normal": "OVA website will serve the following purposes for protecting the integrity of Odia language:-", "002-listElement": "- Odia Virtual Academy website has been launched to digitize and preserve rare Odia books, lexicon, ancient magazines-journals, traditional music, ancient documents and literature on science and history.", "003-listElement": "- Moreover folk culture, tribal language and literature, history-oriented essays, speech of great personalities, Sri Jagannath culture, temple and architectures would also be preserved.", "004-listElement": "- This website will preserve the contributions of poets, writers, playwrights, journalists, critics, translators and literary stalwarts, all those people who have enriched and protected the treasure of Odia language.", "005-listElement": "- OVA website will work and promote the recent trend of computer and internet based application of language resources.", "006-listElement": "- This website will ensure simple and easy use of Odia language in computers, and will be helpful for relevant research work by govt/private organizations, institutions, academies and universities.", "007-normal": "OVA website will develop an internet based dictionary, thesaurus, encyclopaedia in Odia though vocabulary and grammar are important for any language."}}